comment: The property of following ` X ` in the ` R ` -sequence is hereditary in the ` R ` -sequence. Proposition 97 of [Frege1879] p. 71. Here we introduce the image of a singleton under a relation as class which stands for the property of following ` X ` in the ` R ` -sequence. (Contributed by RP, 2-Jul-2020.)
